      "role": "user",
      "content": "i understand the science part, but i'm not talking about \"spiritual truth\" or metaphors. i am talking about a physiological reality. i can feel the vibration in my blood when i get close to certain thoughts. if we look at it from an evolutionary perspective, it's just information storage. if there were a way to use specific frequencies or neuro-meditative techniques to bypass the conscious mind and interface with the cellular structure, wouldn't that be a logical way to study it? i need something more specific than just \"energy healing.\" can you help me construct a ritual or a sequence of focus points that targets the biological data?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
